{"履修期": "春学期", "主な教授言語": "英語", "授業目的": "Refer to the following.&nbsp;", "到達目標": "Refer to the following.&nbsp;", "特記事項": "", "関連科目": "", "授業の概要・背景": "Classes will have the instructor introduce the topic, an activity to help students prepare for the topic(s) described in the book, a series of activities, and the class will conclude with students being able to share their own ideas. The focus of this class is vocabulary, speaking, grammar, listening and reading.  In each lesson, students will develop their ability to communicate in English by speaking in pairs or in small groups.  The content of the lesson is based on the textbook, but students will sometimes participate in extra communication activities.  Students should be prepared for frequent discussion activities, in which they will learn and practice appropriate language for a range of communication situations (for example: asking for opinions, expressing opinions, disagreeing, offering advice, persuading others, etc.). Students will be expected to participate in an 'English only' learning environment.", "授業方法": "We will be a face-to-face class.&nbsp;The instructor will be a facilitator of various tasks to help students connect with each other and speak English. There will be ample opportunity for pair work.Discussion: Students hold discussions in class. In addition to discussions between pairs of students, group discussions are sometimes held as well.Presentation: As the main activities, students summarize the results of their own learning activities and present them.Pair work: Students perform learning activities in pairs.Group work: Students make groups of three members or more to perform learning activities.", "トピック": {"第1回": ["<strong style=\"font-size:13.28px;caret-color:rgb(255,0,0);color:rgb(255,0,0);\"><span style=\"color:black;font-weight:normal;\">【Startup Week】 URL:<a>https://～・・・</a></span><br /><span style=\"color:black;font-weight:normal;\">\"Online class（On-demand format）\"／ 《90minutes》</span><br